# .gitignore
# Platform-managed starter .gitignore. project_owned in practice — edit freely.

# --- Agent / harness local state (never commit) ---
.opencode/state/
.opencode/sessions/
.opencode/plans/
.opencode/runs/
.opencode/scripts/__pycache__/
.local/coordinator/
.local/config/
.local/ssh/
.local/demo-server/

# --- Local operator coordination / task registry (private) ---
.local/coordinator/

# --- Repo-scoped scratch (agent runs, logs, temp) ---
tmp/
*.log
*.tmp
*.bak

# --- Python caches / test artifacts ---
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.pytest_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.mypy_cache/
htmlcov/
.coverage
coverage.*
*.egg-info/

# --- Node (web/admin) ---
node_modules/
.next/
.turbo/
dist/

# --- Env files (never commit secrets) ---
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
*.env
# (env EXAMPLES are tracked)
!*.env.example
!*.env.*.example

# --- Harness config docs ---
# The harness does NOT scatter *.example scaffolds here. Run
# `vh-agent-harness example <path>` to print a file's doc/template on demand
# (e.g. `vh-agent-harness example .vh-agent-harness/AGENTS.mission.md`).

# --- auto-classifier-pilot config (per-developer + secrets-adjacent) ---
# Config files live under .opencode/repo-configs/. Three kinds, two rules:
#   1. CONVENTION local-companions (gitignored): the optional `.local.json`
#      shallow field-override beside each committed base file. auto-gate is the
#      first consumer. The scoped wildcard keeps these per-developer and out of
#      history without over-matching files outside repo-configs/.
#   2. The SECRETS LLM file (gitignored): auto-gate-llm.json is NEVER committed
#      (secrets-adjacent — model endpoint/key). Only the LLM file is ignored by
#      its bare name; the behavior-config base (auto-gate-config.json) is NOT
#      ignored — it is the optionally-committable shared base.
#   3. COMMITTED base files (NOT gitignored): X.json files under repo-configs/
#      are intended to be committed when they encode shared project policy.
.opencode/repo-configs/*.local.json
.opencode/repo-configs/auto-gate-llm.json

# --- Editor / OS ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
.idea/
.vscode/
